### Problem Description

This bug report comes from [Elasticsearch discuss forum](https://discuss.elastic.co/t/term-aggregation-ordering-within-a-pivot-transform/351754).

`"order"` parameter ([docs](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/search-aggregations-bucket-terms-aggregation.html#_ordering_by_the_term_value)) is ignored when specified in the `"aggregations"` section of a transform.
It works fine when specified in the search request (outside of transform).

